  "code": "%% Tombstone timeline and shadowing\n%% Alt: Timeline of writes, tombstones, TTL expiry across generations\n%% Caption: Newer writes can shadow older tombstones; TTLs expire visibility over time\nsequenceDiagram\n  participant W1 as Write v=42, t=1000\n  participant T1 as RowTombstone t=2000\n  participant W2 as Write v=new, t=3000\n  participant TTL as TTL Expiry\n\n  Note over W1: value 42 visible until T1\n  T1->>W1: Deletes older value(IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic)\n  Note over W2: newer value writes after T1\n  TTL-->>W2: Optional expiry at t=write+ttl\n\n",
